Southfield, Michigan, United States



Key people

Carl Icahn, Chairman of the Board
Rainer Jückstock, CEO, Federal-Mogul Powertrain
Brad Norton, CEO, Federal-Mogul Motorparts


Products
Pistons, Rings, Pins, Liners, Valve Seats and Guides, Ignition, Bearings, Bushings, Heat shields, Sealing, Systems Protection, Transmission, Brake, Chassis, Wiper products


Revenue
 US$7.317 billion (2014)[1]



